sequenceDiagram
    actor Reporter
    participant API as api-service (IncidentResource/Service)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant K as Kafka (incident-created)
    participant AN as analyzer-service

    Reporter->>API: POST /incidents
    API->>DB: save Incident (synchronous)
    API-->>Reporter: 200 OK + created Incident
    API->>K: publish IncidentCreatedEvent (fire-and-forget)

    Note over API,Reporter: Response already returned -- publish does not block creation

    K->>AN: consume incident-created
    AN->>DB: similarity(title||description) > 0.4 against other open incidents
    alt likely duplicate found
        AN->>DB: persist Comment("Possible duplicate of incident #X")
    else no match
        AN->>AN: log "no likely duplicate found"
    end
